uima.cas.Sofa.sofaString: INDICATION: Intermittent chest pain, evaluate for pneumonia. CHEST, PA AND LATERAL: Mild pleural parenchymal scarring is present at the lung apices. There is patchy bibasilar atelectasis, without focal consolidation. Mild degenerative changes in the bilateral acromioclavicular joints.
